response.overview: The 2025 NXT Deadline (stylized as DEADL1NE), also promoted as NXT Deadline: San Antonio, is an upcoming professional wrestling livestreaming event produced by WWE. It will be the fourth annual Deadline held for wrestlers from the promotion's developmental brand NXT. The event will take place on Saturday, December 6, 2025, at the Boeing Center at Tech Port in San Antonio, Texas and will be the first Deadline to broadcast on Netflix in international markets. The event is based around the Iron Survivor Challenge for men and women, a 25-minute five-person match in which a wrestler attempts to score the most falls in order to win and earn a match for the NXT Championship and NXT Women's Championship, respectively.
response.title: NXT Deadline 2025
